{"tid":1003901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企有個行動唔方便嘅屋企人入一入黎","createTime":"2019-02-01T04:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T10:06:29.000Z","uid":137726,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d291eafa1b13968a8e3a34a9a36e5668dd093a3e","tid":1003901,"uid":137726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T04:46:03.000Z","msg":"頭先睇到新聞見到政府原來係可以資助殘疾人士乘坐專用的無障礙的士，屌你老母鬼唔望你全家黎緊十世都要坐輪椅，一日到黑係度做show ，知唔知幾多殘疾人士要你幫手，每日150搞到醫院爆哂，已經有好多人需要嘅醫療服務俾班蝗搶撚哂。你連資助殘疾人士坐無障礙的士果小小錢都仲要等？<br />\n望住屋企湊大自己嘅屋企人行動唔方便搞到咁辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n見到林鄭條八婆小小事都唔撚做真係好撚嬲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">調查顯示，有約82%受訪者同意政府應資助殘疾人士乘坐專用的無障礙的士。</span></span><a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2051475/%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%3A%E9%80%BE%E5%85%AD%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E6%8C%87%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E8%B3%AA%E7%B4%A0%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2051475%2F%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%253A%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258B%2599%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%25B4%25A0%25E8%2589%25AF%25E5%25A5%25BD&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=ec72113a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2051475/%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%3A%E9%80%BE%E5%85%AD%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E6%8C%87%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E8%B3%AA%E7%B4%A0%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD</a>"},{"pid":"b90f290362566f72901e74de394b9b2c06e10a3a","tid":1003901,"uid":188145,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T04:57:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ccdf27f5ab0259ee554d648eed4290d4a081f78d","tid":1003901,"uid":223656,"lik